Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.34,0:01:58.80,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5}第二 衝破蛋殼 世界將無限寬廣
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.52,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}妳扣動正義的扳機
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.06,0:02:10.48,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFEAD7&}散發異樣的情感 讓我厭惡
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.86,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H42&}妳總是找著悲傷藉口
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.86,0:02:19.24,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&H42&}扮演著女主角 讓我憎恨
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.36,0:02:23.45,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5\3a&H7E&}淚水根本不適合妳吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.87,0:02:27.87,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A2F2&\blur5\3a&H24&\bord2}鏡子裡真正的我
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.54,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}一事無成且原地踏步
