Comment: 1,0:03:08.70,0:03:12.50,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}Slash your tears away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.96,0:03:18.26,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我不會再逃避
